summary: Fixes a bug preventing the quest \"Throat of the World\" to start just after \"Alduin\'t Wall\"
descriptionHtml:
If you have finished the quest \"Alduin\'s Wall\", but no quest starts after that download this mod and enter in the console \"setstage mq204 10\".

To install it, just decompress it and move the esp file and the Scripts folder in your Skyrim / Data folder.

Please let me know if you have any issue in the quest \"Throat of the World\" that may be caused by this mod.
author: WitchRiser AKA VitchRazor
